data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 18, 2026</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104nsk1665702739767.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nsk1665702739767.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nsk1665702739767.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"nsk1665702739767\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Including Assignment Files\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Within an assignment file, you can use the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#FILE</span> directive to include the contents of another assignment file.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nsk1665702739767__section_w7228ab1b5b1_w7229ab1b5_w7230ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d204675e54\">\n                  \n Syntax\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"nsk1665702739767__p_d29984e1_d29985e1_d29986e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#FILE</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">FileName</var>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"nsk1665702739767__p_d29987e1_d29988e1_d29989e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">FileName</var>—name of the assignment file to include</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nsk1665702739767__section_w7231ab1b5b3_w7232ab1b5_w7233ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d204675e75\">\n                  \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"nsk1665702739767__p_d29993e1_d29994e1_d29995e1\">The file named on a <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#FILE</span> directive is not copied into the current assignment file. It is handled as a separate assignment file and must have a section header on the first non-comment line. After processing the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#FILE</span> directive, processing in the parent assignment file continues in the current section there.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"nsk1665702739767__p_d29996e1_d29997e1_d29998e1\">Multiple <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#FILE</span> directives are allowed.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nsk1665702739767__section_vq4_ml5_qcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d204675e96\">Example: #FILE</h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">For example, running an application in character mode requires a\n               special group of settings for widget mappings. Default settings for character mode\n               are contained in the file <span class=\"ph filepath\">usyschr.asn</span> which is included in the\n               distribution kit.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">To include the definitions in this file, use the following\n               directive:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"nsk1665702739767__pre_tr4_nl5_qcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">#FILE USYSADM:usyschr.asn</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nsk1665702739767__section_qjz_jq1_4cc\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table frame-all\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"nsk1665702739767__table_evy_ypg_q3c\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Related learning videos</span></caption><colgroup><col style=\"width:50%\"/><col style=\"width:50%\"/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"nsk1665702739767__table_evy_ypg_q3c__entry__1\">Title</th>\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"nsk1665702739767__table_evy_ypg_q3c__entry__2\">link</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"nsk1665702739767__table_evy_ypg_q3c__entry__1\">Using Assignment File #file directive</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"nsk1665702739767__table_evy_ypg_q3c__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"https://vimeo.com/1164713410\" rel=\"external noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"Watch or listen Using Assignment File #file directive video\" class=\"image\" id=\"nsk1665702739767__image_nvt_tfg_q3c\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/My_Video_Button.jpg?_LANG=enus\"/></a></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wyr1665702739836.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>usyschr.asn</a><p>The usyschr.asn file contains default widget settings for the character mode interface.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530407\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530407\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Including Assignment Files Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 18, 2026 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Including Assignment Files Within an assignment file, you can use the #FILE directive to include the contents of another assignment file. Syntax #FILE FileName FileName —name of the assignment file to include Description The file named on a #FILE directive is not copied into the current assignment file. It is handled as a separate assignment file and must have a section header on the first non-comment line. After processing the #FILE directive, processing in the parent assignment file continues in the current section there. Multiple #FILE directives are allowed. Example: #FILE For example, running an application in character mode requires a special group of settings for widget mappings. Default settings for character mode are contained in the file usyschr.asn which is included in the distribution kit. To include the definitions in this file, use the following directive: #FILE USYSADM:usyschr.asn Copy Table 1. Related learning videos Title link Using Assignment File #file directive Related Links usyschr.asn The usyschr.asn file contains default widget settings for the character mode interface. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}